OL,3,CShoreham Airshow disaster pilot's
OL,4,Clicence appeal turned down again
OL,6,FThe pilot who crashed at the Shoreham
OL,7,FAirshow ten years ago, killing 11 men,
OL,8,Fhas failed in his final attempt to be
OL,9,Fallowed to fly again.
OL,11,FAndy Hill, who survived the disaster
OL,12,Fin 2015, challenged a Civil Aviation
OL,13,FAuthority decision not to restore his
OL,14,Flicence.
OL,16,FA coroner blamed him for the crash at
OL,17,Fan inquest in 2022, after an Old
OL,18,FBailey jury cleared him of
OL,19,Fmanslaughter in 2019.
