OL,3,CShoreham Airshow disaster pilot's
OL,4,Clicence appeal turned down again
OL,6,FMr Hill appealed against the Civil
OL,7,FAviation Authority decision not to
OL,8,Frestore his flying licence.
OL,10,FTheir decision not to let him fly
OL,11,Fagain was upheld following a two day
OL,12,Fhearing last year.
OL,14,FFor a second time, the pilot started
OL,15,Fthe process of apply for a Judicial
OL,16,FReview of the CAA refusal to let him
OL,17,Ffly again.
OL,19,FFamilies of the men who died ten years
OL,20,Fago were told on Friday (9 May) the
OL,21,Fapplication has been turned down.
