OL,3,CShoreham Airshow disaster pilot's
OL,4,Clicence appeal turned down again
OL,6,FBob and Caroline Schilt said: "We are
OL,7,Fgreatly relieved to hear that Andrew
OL,8,FHill has been refused the opportunity
OL,9,Fto take out a judicial review against
OL,10,Fthe CAA.
OL,12,F"We attended the hearing in London at
OL,13,Fwhich the CAA explained their
OL,14,Freasoning for denying Hill his license.
OL,16,F"After the coroner's conclusion found
OL,17,Fthat the eleven men were unlawfully
OL,18,Fkilled due to Hill's diabolical
OL,19,Fflying, it seems to us that justice
OL,20,Fhas finally been served by the refusal
OL,21,Fto renew his license.
