OL,3,CShoreham Airshow disaster pilot's
OL,4,Clicence appeal turned down again
OL,6,F"It has taken 10 years to finally
OL,7,Fbring peace to the eleven families
OL,8,Fwhose lives were torn apart by this
OL,9,Favoidable tragedy."
OL,11,FAnthony Mallinson lost his father,
OL,12,Fretired engineer James Graham
OL,13,FMallinson, in the 2015 disaster.
OL,15,F"We are delighted as a family to hear
OL,16,Fthe news that Mr Hill's latest
OL,17,FJudicial Review against the CAA has
OL,18,Fbeen refused by the High Court and
OL,19,Ftheir decision to revoke all of his
OL,20,Fflying licences will remain unchanged.
