OL,4,Clicence appeal turned down again
OL,6,F"This will hopefully now enable us
OL,7,Fafter nearly 10 years to finally be
OL,8,Fable to grieve for all of our loved
OL,9,Fones in peace and we would now ask Mr
OL,10,FHill to fully respect that."
OL,12,FMatthew Grimstone's dad, Philip, said
OL,13,Fthey believed the CAA were clear
OL,14,FHill's poor flying skills and
OL,15,Fjudgement led to the tragedy.
OL,17,FPhil Grimstone said: "Obviously we are
OL,18,Frelieved and hope that will now be the
OL,19,Fend of this.
