OL,6,F"We believe that there is nothing to
OL,7,Fstop Mr Hill applying for a flying
OL,8,Flicence in another country, given the
OL,9,Freasons the CAA gave for rejecting his
OL,10,Flicences here we hope that he is never
OL,11,Fallowed."
